\c 125
\s IN\nd kosi\nd* iyalondoloza abantu bayo
\d Ingoma yokwenyuka
\p
\v 1 Labo abathembela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni banjengentaba iZiyoni\x + Hlab. 25.2.\x* \add e\add*nganyikinyekiyo\x + Zaga 10.30. Hlab. 10.6.\x*, emi kuze kube phakade\x + Hlab. 122.5.\x*.
\v 2 \add Njenge\add*zintaba ziyiphahlile iJerusalema, ngokunjalo iN\nd kosi\nd* iyabaphahla abantu bayo kusukela kulesisikhathi kuze kube nininini\x + Zek. 2.5.\x*.
\v 3 Ngoba intonga yobukhosi yobubi\x + Zaga 22.8. Isa. 14.5.\x* kayiyikuhlala\x + Eks. 10.14. Isa. 25.10. Isa. 30.30.\x* phezu kwesabelo sabalungileyo\x + Hlab. 16.5.\x*, ukuze abalungileyo bangeluleli izandla zabo kokubi.
\v 4 N\nd kosi\nd*, yenza okuhle kubo abalungileyo\x + Hlab. 119.68.\x* lakubo abaqotho enhliziyweni zabo\x + Hlab. 7.10.\x*.
\v 5 Kodwa labo abaphambukela\x + Jobe 23.11. Hlab. 40.4. 101.3.\x* \add e\add*zindlel\add eni\add* zabo ezitshekileyo\x + Hlu. 5.5. Zaga 2.15.\x* iN\nd kosi\nd* izabenza bahambe labenzi bobubi\x + Hlab. 94.4.\x*. Ukuthula phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + Hlab. 128.6. Gal. 6.16.\x*!